<li  class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3940menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3940 gdlr-normal-menu"><a href="http://www.childrenfirstthesociety.com/our-mission-2/">Our Mission</a></li>
<li  class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3357menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3357 gdlr-normal-menu"><a href="http://www.childrenfirstthesociety.com/our-story/">About Us</a></li>
<li  class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3546menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3546 gdlr-normal-menu"><a href="http://www.childrenfirstthesociety.com/csp/">CSP</a></li>
<li  class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3263menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3263 gdlr-normal-menu"><a href="http://www.childrenfirstthesociety.com/events/">Events</a></li>
<li  class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3254menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3254 gdlr-normal-menu"><a href="http://www.childrenfirstthesociety.com/zakat-donation/">Donate</a></li>
<li  class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3441menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3441 gdlr-normal-menu"><a href="http://www.childrenfirstthesociety.com/contact/">Contact Us</a></li>
