<div class="content-wrapper">
<div class="gdlr-content">
<div class="with-sidebar-wrapper"><section id="content-section-1" ><div class="gdlr-color-wrapper no-skin" style="background-color: #f3f3f3; padding-top: 34px; padding-bottom: 0px; " ><div class="container"><div class="gdlr-item gdlr-slider-item"  style="margin-bottom: -25px;"  ><div class="flexslider" data-pausetime="7000" data-slidespeed="600" data-effect="fade" ><ul class="slides" ><li><img src="http://www.childrenfirstthesociety.com/media/2019/05/Website-banner-1.jpg" alt="" width="1553" height="621" /></li><li><img src="http://www.childrenfirstthesociety.com/media/2019/05/Website-banner-2.jpg" alt="" width="1553" height="621" /></li></ul></div></div><div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="clear"></div></section><section id="content-section-2" ><div class="gdlr-color-wrapper " style="background-color: #ffffff; " ><div class="container"><div class="four columns" ><div class="gdlr-styled-box-item-ux gdlr-ux" ><div class="gdlr-item gdlr-styled-box-item" ><div class="gdlr-styled-box-body" style="background-image: url('http://www.childrenfirstthesociety.com/media/2014/04/style-box-1.jpg'); color: #ffffff; " ><div class="gdlr-styled-box-caption" >Story About Us</div><h3 class="gdlr-styled-box-title" style="color: #ffffff;"><span style="color: #ffffff !important;">Who are we?</span></h3><p><span style="color: #ffffff !important;">We are a unique organization founded in 2006 , wishing to make a difference in the lives of children, the world over. This common goal led to the inception of CFTS.<br />
We have taken it upon ourselves to commit our time and resources to the children who may need the help of sorts from us, be it health or education etc.<br />
</span></p>
</div></div></div></div><div class="eight columns" ><div class="gdlr-styled-box-item-ux gdlr-ux" ><div class="gdlr-item gdlr-styled-box-item" ><div class="gdlr-styled-box-body" style="background-image: url('http://www.childrenfirstthesociety.com/media/2018/04/ps-cfts.jpg'); color: #ffffff; " ><h3 class="gdlr-styled-box-title" style="color: #ffffff;">Our Mission</h3><p><span style="color: #ffffff !important;">Our mission is to provide a better and healthier life to children, who, due to a stroke of misfortune, are unlikely to fulfil their ambition and desires. Our teams are self-motivated towards meeting the aims of the charity in the fields of health and education in Pakistan.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
</div></div></div></div><div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="clear"></div></section><section id="content-section-3" ><div class="gdlr-parallax-wrapper gdlr-background-image no-skin" data-bgspeed="0.1" style="background-image: url('http://www.childrenfirstthesociety.com/media/2014/04/featuremedia-bg.jpg'); padding-top: 110px; padding-bottom: 50px;  border-top: 4px solid #e9e9e9;  border-bottom: 4px solid #e9e9e9; " ><div class="container"><div class="two-fifth columns" ></div><div class="three-fifth columns" ><div class="gdlr-feature-media-ux gdlr-ux"><div class="gdlr-item gdlr-feature-media-item" ><div class="feature-media-content-wrapper"><h3 class="feature-media-title gdlr-skin-title" ><span style="color: #ffffff;">We need your help</span></h3><div class="feature-media-caption gdlr-skin-title" ><span style="color: #ffffff;">Let’s Stop This hunger and fullfill their happiness</span></div><div class="feature-media-content"><p><span style="color: #ffffff;">CFTS actively supports the ICU ward at the National Institute of Children Health (NICH), Karachi. We regularly supply medicines to NICH, particularly those which are required for the treatment of Tetanus, GBS, Steven Johnson and many other diseases pertaining to the ward.<br />
We have been proactively working at the hospital for the past 12 years. Our team would like you to know that we are here to stay committed and driven to achieve our goals – serve children in need of help.<br />
The NICH serves nearly a million patients every year, approximately 50% coming from outside of Karachi mainly the interior Sindh, as well as from lower Punjab and as far as Balochistan, while at the same time it is the only multi-specialty public sector pediatric hospital offering emergency services to the children of this city, over 20 million souls.</span></p>
</div></div></div></div></div><div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="clear"></div></section></div>			<div class="main-content-container container gdlr-item-start-content">
<div class="gdlr-item gdlr-main-content">
